<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">笔记本电池放电过度</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">笔记本电脑电池的续航能力随其使用时间而降低。下面提供几种有助于延长其使用寿命的技术，尽管它们的效果有时并不十分显著。</p>
<div class="list"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ul class="list">
<li class="list"><p class="p">不要让电池过度放电，在电量变得<span class="em">很低</span>前充电，虽然大多数电池都有内置的保护措施，防止过度放电。电量较低时充电效果要好些，而电量损耗不多时充电是有害的。</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">高温会对电池充电有影响，不要让电池太热。</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">Batteries age even if you leave them in storage. There is little
    advantage in buying a replacement battery at the same time as you get the
    original battery — always buy replacements when you need them.</p></li>
</ul></div></div></div>
<div class="note" title="备注">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m4 3h16c0.554 0 1 0.446 1 1v11h-6v6h-11c-0.554 0-1-0.446-1-1v-16c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">此建议尤其适用于锂离子电池，这是最常用的电池类型。其他类型电池的情况可能有所不同。</p></div></div></div>
</div>
